The Telegraph - Calcutta : Bengal

 BRIEFS

 Howrah, Dec. 9: A man in a grey safari suit was found dead off Kona Expressway. Police said there were strangulation marks around the throat of the man in mid-30s. 

 Calcutta: Fr Gerrard Beckers, SJ, of St Xaviers College died on Saturday evening. He was 82. Educated in Belgium, Fr Beckers joined Xaviers as a chemistry lecturer in 1954. 

 Asansol: Speaker Somnath Chatterjee has condemned the incident in which writer- activist Mahasweta Devi led a mob that demolished a pillar for a Santiniketan housing project.




